description:
This is a 57 minute workout called '5000 Steps HIIT: Fat Burning Walk' from the channel Walks Of Life.
The workout falls under Cardio/Walking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Let's stroll and burn some calories with this at-home walking programme that requires 5000 steps to burn fat. This is an aggressive, calorie-burning workout that includes some difficult routines that will engage your abs and keep your heart rate up the entire time, burning more calories.
